title: Taylor Swift’s Tribeca Apartment: Photos of Bad Blood star’s NYC crib |
text:
JUST when you think you couldn’t be more jealous of Taylor Swift, you see pictures of her fabulous warehouse apartment.
The 24-year-old bought the sixth floor penthouse from Lord Of The Rings director Peter Jackson last year for AU$27 million.
Taylor paid AU$27m for the pad. Source: Supplied
It incorporates exposed timber and earthy tones. Source: Supplied
Boasting nine bedrooms and nine bathrooms, the property is reportedly made up of two separate duplexes.
With vaulted ceilings and a gourmet kitchen, the apartment incorporates timber and rust-coloured walls to give a warm, homely feel.
The pad has nine bedrooms and nine bathrooms. Source: Supplied
While this is the first time we’ve been given a decent look inside the 8,018-square-foot pad, it’s quickly become Insta famous — with Tay posting pics of her and her famous gal squad throwing dinner parties and hanging in the loft.
